items.sentence: I'd really like to know why Tom didn't do that.
I'd never have done that if Tom had been there.
I wonder if Tom will figure out how to do that.
I wonder if Tom is still determined to do that.
I wonder if Tom can do that as well as you can.
I told Tom I couldn't do that without his help.
I think we should do that before Tom gets here.
I think Tom will be able to do that eventually.
I should tell Tom that I won't do that anymore.
I knew Tom wouldn't want to do that by himself.
